(8, 3, 'Accounting Assistant', 1, 'Banking, insurances', 'Károly körút 5', 'Budapest', 'Hungary', '2013-05-05', '2014-08-06', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Helping to Befriend The International Terrain&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Cozyfry International is a International Product Launch and Foreign Communications Research Business that helps Entrepreneurs, Small Businesses Owners, Product Inventors and Marketing Companies, Understand and structure their products to the psychology and&nbsp;</span><a id="_GPLITA_0" style="color: #0099d1; font-weight: bold; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" title="Click to Continue &gt; by Browse to Save" href="http://www.internships.com/posting/Accounting-Assistant-I457">purchasing</a><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">&nbsp;habits of unfamiliar culture so that your product&rsquo;s launch produces a lifetime loyalty of the customer, above the high revenue.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Located in Queens, Cozyfry International&rsquo;s secret is that it functions and is run under a team of no more than Four people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Queens community.</span></p>', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-seri