(10, 3, 'SEO, Online Marketing Assistant', 1, 'Banking, insurances', 'pereulok Khlebnyy 14', 'Moscou', 'Russia', '2013-05-03', '2013-09-22', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">With offices in Denver, Colorado and Miami Beach , FL, Fast Internet Marketing offers direct marketing services that have, since 1999, been helping businesses and enterprises make a big impact and big&nbsp;</span><a id="_GPLITA_0" style="color: #0099d1; font-weight: bold; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" title="Click to Continue &gt; by Browse to Save" href="http://www.internships.com/posting/Social-Media-Assistant-I7029">profits online</a><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">. We are fiercely committed to expanding and maturing our clients&rsquo; brand names and market share. For us here at Fast Internet Marketing, our clients&rsquo; return on investment is priority.</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Fast Internet Marketing offers guaranteed online success through the following comprehensive services:</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">&bull; Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'',