 line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">In some rare cases we do allow interns to work on projects together as partners and you may apply as a team. Sometimes we will pair interns to work on large projects together. This internship is unpaid besides equity and performance based bonusses</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Resumes and cover letters can be submitted here or emailed to bvinternships@mutualcatalysis.com</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Feel free&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">to forego sending us a resume and simply write a cover letter telling us why we should interview you.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">We are looking for a variety people with different strengths:</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">-engineering</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">-math</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">-film</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">-management</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">-computer science</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">-sales</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">-music</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">-social skills</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">-marketing</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">The important thing is that you are good at something and generally a hard worker/quick learner. That''s what entrepreneurship is all about.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Master', '3e'),
(13, 0, 'PROTEIN SCIENCE INTERNSHIP', 1, 'Chemistry, pharmacy', '453 S Spring St', 'Los Angeles', 'US', '2013-05-22', '2014-06-20', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Hampton Creek Foods (HCF), is a food technology company headquartered in San Francisco, CA. Put simply, we''re going to transform our food system - even Bill Gates thinks so. He selected us to be in his "Future of Food" documentary, scheduled to be released next month (http://vimeo.com/54495904 pw - hamptoncreekfoods)!&nbsp;</span>\n&nbsp;<span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">We are currently seeking&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">creative, organized, and highly motivated protein research interns with a background in biochemistry, molecular biology, protein chemistry, or a related field. In hiring new interns, we look for people with a self-starting, team-oriented, and interdisciplinary approach to their work. Internships have the potential to develop into permanent, full time positions.</span></p>', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">* Extensive knowledge of ingredient/protein functionality, baked goods is a plus&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">* Strong formulation skills and understanding of food systems&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">* Be curious and passionate about food&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">* Good understanding of sensory testing and statistics, is a plus&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">* Strong communication skills: interpersonal, presentation, oral and written&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">* Highly motivated, critical thinker, goal oriented&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">* Ability to work in a fast paced and high performing environment&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">* Computer Skills: Microsoft Office applications: Word, Excel, Power Point&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Master', '4e'),
(14, 2, 'Arts in Education Internship', 1, 'Banking, insurances', '301 Corporate Pointe', '301 Corporate Pointe\nCulver City', 'US', '2013-05-22', '2015-09-19', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Florida Grand Opera is seeking&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">a part-time education intern, 10-20 hours per week to assist the Director in developing materials, establishing partnerships with schools, and school visits, if possible. Applicants must be available during regular business hours Mon - Fri, 9-5pm; attendance at all Final Dress Rehearsals is required.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">FGO offers one of the most hands-on internships available; you won&rsquo;t be expected to make all the copies (although some of that is part of everyone&rsquo;s&nbsp;job</span><a id="_GPLITA_1" style="color: #0099d1; font-weight: bold; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" title="Click to Continue &gt; by Browse to Save" href="http://www.internships.com/posting/Arts-in-Education-Internship-I8995546"></a><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">). As a member of the Education team you will have the opportunity to work on new initiatives to engage current patrons more deeply and to reach a whole new group of potential opera lovers.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">In the past interns have made public presentations, worked with student groups, planned and managed summer camps, and helped create programming for the department.</span></p>', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Experience in or knowledge of theatre arts administration or education is helpful. Must be outgoing, motivated and hard-working with a great attitude and willingness to learn&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Bachelor', '2e'),
(15, 2, 'Teaching Internship', 1, 'Banking, insurances', 'Jogoo House A, Taifa Rd', 'Nairobi', 'Kenia', '2013-05-22', '2013-06-20', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">In Kenya , income&nbsp;</span><a id="_GPLITA_0" style="color: #0099d1; font-weight: bold; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" title="Click to Continue &gt; by Browse to Save" href="http://www.internships.com/posting/Teaching-Internship-I1202120"></a><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">level creates a large gap amongst school children''s quality of education. Most upper-class children receive exemplary English instruction. However, children of poorer families and communities, who cannot afford expensive English instruction, lag far behind. This lag creates an even larger rift as children progress through their schooling and eventually into the workforce. Opportunities exist for those with strong English skills. IFRE strives to bridge this chasm to offer quality English instruction by collaborating with local rural schools. Intern teachers in Kenya are a prized and welcomed resource! As a teacher intern, you will work in the rural schools mostly work under the direction of the head teacher.</span></p>', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">NO specific skills or qualifications are required. However, some kind of teaching certification or education degree is appreciated. A major in science, math or computer oriented classes is also preferred if you have no teaching education/credentials. Interns must have passion and interest to help children and improve their education.</span></p>', 'Bachelor', '3e'),
(16, 2, 'Education Visionaries', 1, 'Banking, insurances', '281 State Route 79', 'Morganville', 'US', '2013-05-22', '2008-01-01', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Future Teachers of America has developed a new program to help underperforming elementary school students improve their reading and math skills. We recruit and train top high school students to mentor and teach local elementary school students under the guidance of a trained teacher.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Our Internship program will focus on developing a new blended learning course titled &ldquo;Introduction to Teaching and Mentoring for High School Students.&rdquo; This program will introduce top high school students to a career in teaching. It will focus on small group teaching and one-on-one mentoring.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">You will experience the excitement of working at a startup, non-profit company and creating a program that will help younger students to succeed.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">The Future Teachers of America internship is a part-time position with flexible hours. Candidates must be education majors.</span></p>', 'Master', '3e'),
(17, 0, 'Pharmacy Intern', 0, 'Banking, insurances', '625 S Good Latimer Expy W', 'Dallas', 'US', '2013-05-22', '2014-08-31', '<p><strong style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">We are currently accepting applications for a future anticipated opening in this area.</strong><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><strong style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Safeway pharmacists enjoy working in a community pharmacy setting that provides total health care to their neighborhood customers.</strong><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Retail pharmacies provide the most accessible health care resources in the community. Now, more than ever, retail pharmacists are looked to for guidance in managing the total health of their patients.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><br style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Our pharmacists are part of a community where they know their patients by name. With a holistic approach to health care management, our pharmacy staff provides a full compliment of pharmaceutical services in a community pharmacy setting with a workflow model to allow world-class patient care.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<ul style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px